Body:
Abahoze bayobora itorero rya ADEPR, bashinjwa ibyaha birimo kunyereza umutungo wâ€™itorero no gukoresha inyandiko mpimbano, bihannye umucamanza ubaburanisha mu bujurire.
Abahoze bayobora itorero rya ADEPR, bashinjwa ibyaha birimo kunyereza umutungo wâ€™itorero no gukoresha inyandiko mpimbano, bihannye umucamanza ubaburanisha mu bujurire.
Abaregwa ni Sibomana Jean, Tom Rwagasana, Mutuyemariya Christine, Sebagabo Leonard, Sindayigaya Theophile, Gasana Valens, Niyitanga Straton, Beninka Bertin, Mukabera Lynea, Twizerimana Emmanuel, Nzabarinda Tharcisse na Mukakamari Mediatrice.
Ubushinjacyaba bubarega kunyereza 2 366 708 946Frw nkâ€™uko byagaragajwe muri raporo yâ€™umugenzuzi yakozwe nyuma yâ€™ifatwa ryâ€™abo bayobozi mu 2017.
Ku wa 14 Ukuboza 2018 nibwo Urukiko Rwisumbuye rwa Gasabo, Urugereko ruburanisha ibyaha bimunga ubukungu bwâ€™igihugu, rwagize abere Bishop Sibomana Jean na Bishop Tom Rwagasana bari abayobozi ba ADEPR nâ€™abandi 10 kuko batahamwe nâ€™ibyaha bari bakurikiranyweho.
Ubuyobozi bwa ADEPR nâ€™ubushinjacyaha bwajuririye iki cyemezo mu Urukiko Rukuru, ari naho urubanza rugeze kuri ubu.
Urubanza rukimara kujuririrwa abaregwa bagiye bitaba urukiko urubanza rugasubikwa kugeza ubwo rwongeye gusubukurwa tariki ya 21/2/201/20 saa mbili za mugitondo ku Rukiko Rukuru, aho ababurana bose bari bitabiriye ndetse bafite nâ€™ababunganira mu mategeko.
Ubushinjacyaha bwabwiye urukiko ko bwasabye Urwego rwâ€™Imiyoborere (RGB) gukora ubugenzuzi (Audit) kandi ko irimo kubikora nkâ€™uko biri mu ibaruwa umushinjacyaha yasomeye urukiko yanditswe na RGB, akomeza asaba ko urubanza rwashyirwa tariki ya 8/7/2020.
Uku kongera gusubika urubanza byatumye uwari umuvugizi wa ADEPR, Bishop Sibomana Jean, avuga ko urubanza rumaze gusubikwa inshuro zirindwi zose hashakwa ibimenyetso, agaragaza ko izo nshuro nta na rimwe atitabye urukiko bityo ko atumva impamvu akomeza kubura ubutabera.
Yakomeje avuga ko imitungo ye yose kimwe nâ€™iyâ€™abandi batandatu [Tom Rwagasana, Sebagabo Leonard, Mutuyemariya Christine, Niyitanga Salton, Sindayigaya Theophile na Gasana Valens] yafatiriwe bikabagiraho ingaruka zikomeye mu gihe ku bandi batanu bareganwa itafatiriwe ndetse bari mu kazi ka ADEPR.
Bishop Sibomana yavuze ko urubanza rumaze gusubikwa kuva tariki ya 10/6/2019, 18/6/2019, 17/7/2019, 6/9/2019, 13/9/2019, 03/10/2019, 8/11/2019, 21/2/2020; atigeze abura mu rukiko, akabishingiraho asaba ko umucamanza uyoboye iburanisha witwa Nzabonimana Cassien ava mu rubanza kuko uko gutinda akubona nko kubogama ku ruhande rumwe rurega kuko ari rwo ruhora rusaba ko urubanza rusubikwa hagishakishwa ibimenyetso.
Abaregwa bavuga ko ubugenzuzi bwasabwe nâ€™ubucamanza batemeranya na bwo kuko mu 2017 hari ubwakoreshejwe nâ€™ubushinjacyaha bukaburanirwaho mu rukiko rwisumbuye rwa Gasabo. Kuba rero harasabwe ubundi bugenzuzi nyuma yâ€™imyaka itatu batari mu kazi babibona nko kubaheza mu gihirahiro.
Ubwihane bwâ€™umucamanza bukaba bwaratanzwe kuri uyu wa Mbere kugira ngo busuzumwe nâ€™urukiko. Urubanza rukaba ruzasubukurwa nyuma yuko urukiko rufashe icyemezo kuri ubwo bwihane.
Ni ryari umuburanyi yihana umucamanza?
Kwihana umucamanza ni igihe umuburanyi yanze ko amuburanisha iyo;
Ubwe cyangwa uwo bashakanye nâ€™abana babo, bafite inyungu bwite mu rubanza;
Ubwe, cyangwa uwo bashakanye afitanye isano yâ€™amaraso cyangwa yo gushyingiranwa ku buryo butaziguye cyangwa afitanye isano ku buryo buziguye kugeza ku gisanira cya kane nâ€™umwe mu bagize inteko yâ€™urukiko, nâ€™umwe mu baburanyi, nâ€™umwunganira cyangwa umuhagarariye;
Umwe mu baburanyi agaragaje ishingiro ryâ€™urwango afitanye nâ€™umucamanza;
Umwe mu baburanyi agaragaje ko umucamanza afitanye ubucuti bwihariye nâ€™undi mu baburanyi cyangwa kuva aho urubanza rutangiriye, yarigeze kwakirwa mu buryo bwihariye nâ€™umwe mu baburanyi ku mafaranga ye, cyangwa yaremeye impano ahawe nâ€™umuburanyi;
Iyo yigeze kugira icyo avuga cyangwa agatanga inama kuri urwo rubanza mbere yâ€™uko ruburanishwa;
Iyo yigeze kuba mu rubanza ari umucamanza, umwunzi, umushinjacyaha, umugenzacyaha, umuburanyi, umutangabuhamya, , umusemuzi, inzobere cyangwa umukozi wo mu butegetsi bwa Leta;
Yiyamwa kandi iyo habayeho urubanza rwâ€™ishinjabyaha cyangwa rwâ€™imbonezamubano, hagati yâ€™umucamanza cyangwa uwo bashakanye, abafitanye nâ€™umucamanza isano ishingiye ku maraso cyangwa ku gushyingirwa ku buryo butaziguye cyangwa ku buryo buziguye kugeza ku gisanira cya kane nâ€™umwe mu baburana, uwo bashakanye cyangwa abo bafitanye isano ishingiye ku maraso cyangwa ku gushyingirwa ku buryo butaziguye cyangwa ku buryo buziguye kugeza ku gisanira cya kane.
